<i>adverb</i>: 엄숙히 [엄수키], 숙연히 [수견히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄숙히 [엄수키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. solemnly; gravely; seriously</dd><br>
<dd>의식이나 분위기 등이 무겁고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a ceremony, atmosphere, etc., being heavy and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>2. solemnly; gravely; seriously</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 태도 등이 무겁고 점잖게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a speech, attitude, etc., being heavy and refined.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>숙연히 [수견히]</dt><br>
<dd>solemnly</dd><br>
<dd>고요하고 엄숙하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and gravely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>